message.body: What colors the kitchen gonan be?
Walls are going to be a soft yellow.. painting the counter tops and cabinets with decorative paint. Black/brown countertops and birch colored cabinets
You're painting the countertops? That's interesting

Lol the house, especially the kitchen is old fashion. The counter tops are just the plain sheet like mom and dad have. We wanted marble tops but that is expensive so we are painting it marble instead. That's the decorative paint
